# AI Services Ownership

## Overview

This directory contains the core AI and machine learning service implementations for the Helix project.

## Primary Owners

- **Team**: `@ai-team`
- **Backup Team**: `@ml-engineers`

## Scope

- AI provider integrations (OpenAI, Anthropic)
- LLM service coordination
- AI analysis algorithms
- Prompt engineering and optimization

## Files and Responsibilities

### Base AI Provider (`base_ai_provider.dart`)
- **Owners**: `@ai-team`, `@backend-team`
- **Description**: Abstract base class for all AI providers
- **Critical**: Yes - Changes affect all AI integrations

### OpenAI Provider (`openai_provider.dart`)
- **Owners**: `@ai-team`, `@ml-engineers`
- **Description**: OpenAI GPT-4 integration
- **API Keys Required**: Yes
- **Dependencies**: OpenAI API

### AI Coordinator (`ai_coordinator.dart`)
- **Owners**: `@ai-team`, `@backend-team`
- **Description**: Coordinates AI service calls and provider failover
- **Critical**: Yes - Central orchestration logic

## Review Guidelines

### Required Reviews
- All changes require at least **1 approval** from `@ai-team`
- API changes require **2 approvals** from `@ai-team` and `@backend-team`
- Changes to base classes require `@helix-maintainers` review

### Testing Requirements
- Unit tests for all provider implementations
- Integration tests with mocked API responses
- Error handling and failover scenarios
- Performance benchmarks for latency-critical paths

### Security Considerations
- API keys must never be committed
- All API calls must use secure HTTPS
- Rate limiting must be respected
- User data privacy must be maintained

## Key Metrics

- **Response Time**: < 2 seconds for standard analysis
- **Success Rate**: > 99% (with failover)
- **Test Coverage**: > 90%

## Dependencies

- `dart:convert` - JSON serialization
- `http` package - API requests
- Service locator pattern - Dependency injection

## Related Documentation

- [AI Services API Documentation](/docs/AI_SERVICES_API.md)
- [Architecture Documentation](/docs/Architecture.md)
- [Testing Strategy](/docs/TESTING_STRATEGY.md)

## Escalation

For urgent issues or architectural questions:
1. Tag `@ai-team` in PR/issue
2. Contact AI team lead via Slack `#helix-ai-team`
3. Escalate to `@helix-maintainers` if needed

